PrecisEnactment of an ORDER AMENDING MILK ORDERS UNDER THE AGRICULTURAL PRODUCTS MARKETING ACT which amends the definition of milk in various Orders delegating authority to provincial milk marketing boards to regulate the marketing of fluid milk in interprovincial trade, in order to specify that it is "for consumer use in liquid form".
